    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Provide support to help access international and bilateral climate finance for adaptation Investment in strengthening information management, early warning, adaptation, local level communications to reach at risk communities to prepare them against shocks Using innovation science and technology to implement forecast based early actions including insurance, forecasting and risk communication and nature-based solutions for adaptation Implementation of shock responsive social protection guidelines.Strengthening of information systems - integrtaed social registry, bipad protal Provide TA facility based with ministry of finance and working across GoN stakeholders at three speheres of government Sytem strengthening across federal, provincial and local government to improve coordination to implement policies and plans on climate adaptation and disaster risk management"
      },
